# Runtime dependencies for a reproducible, hash-verified install.
# Pinned to the tested set (mirrors constraints.txt). Regenerate the lock with:
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements.lock requirements.in
#
# NOTE: requirements.lock here was generated on Windows / CPython 3.12. It
# installs cleanly on Linux/macOS too (the only platform-specific entries,
# colorama and win32-setctime, ship universal pure-Python wheels), but for
# marker-precise locks per OS, regenerate it on each target platform (or run
# pip-compile in a CI matrix).
